prodNameC: 貝爾斯5-羥引朵醋酸試劑 (未滅菌)
ingredientsDesc:
1. Reagent. 1 x 500 mL. Hydrochloric acid 0.1 mol/L.
2. Reagnet. 1 x 200 mL. Ammonia 20 mmol/L.
3. Microcolumns. 2 x 20 mL. Contain a pre-weighted amount of a buffered neutral resin.
A. Reagent. 1 x 100 mL. Sulfuric acid 1 mol/L.
B. Reagent. 1 x .100 mL. 1-Nitroso-2-naphtol 6 mmol/L, ethanol 99%.
C. Reagnet. 1 x 5 mL. Sodium nitrite 0.7 mol/L.
D. Reagent. 1 x 280 mL. Dichloroethane.
E. Standard. 1 x 20 mL. Serotonin 46.1 mg/L equivalent to 50 mg/L=261 μmol/L of  5-HIAA, hydrochloric acid 0.1 mol/L, preservative.
applicantAddr: 新北市板橋區民生路三段299巷13號4樓
efficacy: 測量5-羥引朵醋酸濃度用試劑。
